data.description: This beautiful country home has it all! Situated on just over 5 acres of land, with an in-ground salt water pool, firepit, storage buildings, 2 car garage and so much room! Inside you have plenty of space to spread out with over 2500 square feet! The main level features 3 bedrooms, with a split floorpan. The master suite has duel sinks, soaker tub and shower and large walk-in closet. With the open floor plan, enjoy a spacious kitchen with pantry, seating at the bar and open dining area. All kitchen appliances will remain! Upstairs you have so many options for uses! There is a third full bathroom, open flex space that could be used for game room, media space, family room, or perfect hangout for your teens! There's also a bonus room/office with a closet upstairs that current owners are using as a 4th bedroom. If you have been looking for space in the country to find a slower pace, have room to run and play and enjoy sunsets on your back deck, then don't miss this property!
